metadata.name: Anim-AI
metadata.description: Anim-AI is a pfp collection of anime characters created using AI.  All pieces are 1 of 1 editions. There will be 100 pieces in total, released in batches of 10.  The first 10 will grant holders 50% discount to future drops, and after they are sold out there will be a drawing for 0.2 ethereum!  All 100 pieces will grant early access to future drops!
